<plot>Eddie's brother-in-law Wally comes for a visit, and when Eddie's wife goes away, Wally disrupts him every minute. The new television set is delivered and Wally decides to erect the aerial and install it himself and used the money saved to throw a party. Despite nearly wrecking the house, Wally throws the party anyway, and Eddie joins in...until his wife comes home and catches him dancing with a girl friend of Wally's.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?240799</url></doc>
